2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> In TRV</span><hr size=1> ::After stabbleing Argo II,Xena wanders the tribe until coming across a hut that was given to her. She walks up to the door and pushes the door open,then steps inside. She takes a look around. Walking to the bedroom she lights the candle that sat on a small table by the bed. She places her hands on her hips as she looks around the room:: Works for me....:: She mumbles to herself,then goes about stripping off her armor and weapon. She sets her armor on a chair then leans her sword up against the wall by the chair.Looks at her stuff,her chakram wasn't there. Gabrielle still had it,or so Xena hoped. She sighs then walks over to the bed and sits down on it::<br>
<br>
::Her eyes drift across the room before settling on the candle flame on the small table. She lays down,staring at the flame. She brings her arms up under her head,then slowly takes her eyes off the flame and looks up at the ceiling. She lets out another heavy sigh as she stares up at the ceiling:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=amazonprincessraven>Amazon Princess Raven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(12/22/01 4:47:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A new sister</span><hr size=1> There was a knock on Xena's door. As Yakut was still with Glory in her own hut, it was Raven's job to do the &quot;Queenly&quot; things around the village.<br>
<br>
&quot;Xena?&quot;<br>
<br>
The young amazon questioned towards the door. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uheroicxena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Heroic Xena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(12/22/01 5:59:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/heroicxena/images/xena-2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A new sister</span><hr size=1> ::At the sound of the knock,Xena pulled herself off the bed and walked to the door. She glances back a moment to her sword. Then shakes her head. What do I need my sword for? She asked herself. Course she doesnt need her sword. Always too cautious she thought of herself,then turned once more to the door and swung it open. She quirks a brow as she looks at Raven.::<br>
<br>
::Not having met Raven before. A simple...:: Hey.... ::Was given as she looks at Raven.:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=amazonprincessraven>Amazon Princess Raven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(12/23/01 1:32:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hmm</span><hr size=1> Raven quirked a light brow at the greeting. Raven pushed forward in her arms a bundle of skins and leathers.<br>
<br>
&quot;The Queen wished for these to be brought to you. It's going to be a cold winter in the North this year.&quot;<br>
<br>
The skins were of various animals of the North.<br>
<br>
&quot;The ancients have blessed us with many creatures this fall. We were able to bring back food and clothing to survive the cold.&quot;<br>
<br>
The ancients, hopefully Xena knew about them. Raven had heard stories about her and Gabrielle going to another tribe up North before, but they might not know that much. Especially being so close to Olympian grounds before.<br>
<br>
&quot;We're having a fireside later this evening if you wish to join us, you are welcome to.&quot;<br>
<br>
Raven had a darkness about her. She held the amazons and women in greatest honor and respect, but in her eyes there was no mercy towards men. Unlike her mother Yakut, Raven wished for the ancient days. Yakut had a kind peaceful heart, Raven was serious and determined for glory towards her mothers and tribes name. <br>
<br>
As she turned to leave, she looked back once more.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'm Prigkipissa Raven by the way. Yakut's eldest daughter.&quot;<br>
<br>
She then turned to go and begin preparations for the fireside. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uheroicxena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Heroic Xena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(12/29/01 12:07:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/heroicxena/images/xena-2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hmm</span><hr size=1> ::Xena takes the bundle of leathers and skins.:: Thanks.<br>
<br>
Glad to meet you,Raven. ::She nodded:: Maybe i'll see ya at the fireside later.....::If she went. She wasnt much for sitting around a fire with a bunch of people she most likely didnt know. As Raven turns to leave. Xena nudges the door closed with her foot,then wanders back over to her bed. Tossing the blankets on the bed then laying herself back down on the bed.:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ufaithamznprincess21.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FaithAmznPrincess21</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(1/20/02 9:13:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: new sister</span><hr size=1> :not wanting to bother Xena she gently places the basket of food and ale: I hope she likes these<br>
:there is a note from her:<br>
:gently knocks on the door to get the warrior's attention:<br>
<br>
Note reads:<br>
Welcome to Tanais River Valley<br>
I hope u stay with us a long time. <br>
my name is Faith if u need anything I am in this village mostly ever day. I am the advisor to the princess. Please just ask for me.<br>
this basket is for u. i hope u like it i made most of it myself. <br>
well see u around the valley<br>
<br>
Faith Othe Wind Advisor to the Princess <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uheroicxena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Heroic Xena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(1/24/02 11:58:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re:</span><hr size=1> Having just barely drifted off to sleep,Xena was awoken by the knock at her door. She sits up then pulls herself away from the bed. &quot;This better be good...&quot; She mumbles to herself as she made her way to the door. She pulls the door open and looks outside just intime to see Faith already leaving. <br>
<br>
She glances down,seeing the basket,then grabs the note and reads it. Looks up again toward Faith. &quot;Hey,Faith!&quot; Waves for her to come back if and when Faith turns to see her.<br>
<br>
As she waits,she grabs the basket and moves over to the bench outside of her hut and sits down on it. Not going to get any sleep anytime soon,might aswell enjoy whats left of the day and maybe some company.<br>
<br>
After looking through the basket of goodys,she sets it down by the bench. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ufaithamznprincess21.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FaithAmznPrincess21</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(1/27/02 9:47:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> :waves at Xena walking back over with her staff in her hand:sorry if i disturbed u i just wanted to give that as a welcome gift. hope u like them <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uheroicxena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Heroic Xena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(1/30/02 1:22:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re:</span><hr size=1> Xena stands up as Faith comes back over.<br>
<br>
&quot;It's alright.&quot; Smiles some<br>
<br>
&quot;I just wanted to thank you for the gift...thanks.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ufaithamznprincess21.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FaithAmznPrincess21</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(1/30/02 11:01:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> :smiles as she nods to xena:your welcome. I just wanted to do something nice. <br>
